.TH THEMECTL-EXPORT 1 "2024" "themectl" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
themectl export \- export theme to specific format
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B themectl export
\fITHEME\fR \fIFORMAT\fR [\fIOPTIONS\fR]
.PP
.B themectl export
\fITHEME\fR all [\fIOPTIONS\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Export a theme to a specific application format or all formats at once.
.PP
Supported formats: kitty, waybar, neovim, starship, mako, hyprland,
hyprpaper, wofi, wlogout, fastfetch, nix, yazi
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.BR \-\-output \fIPATH\fR
Output file path (or directory if exporting all formats)
.TP
.BR \-\-all
Export all formats at once (alternative to "all" format name)
.SH EXAMPLES
Export to Kitty format:
.RS
.PP
themectl export gruvbox-dark kitty
.RE
.PP
Export to file:
.RS
.PP
themectl export gruvbox-dark kitty --output kitty.conf
.RE
.PP
Export all formats to directory:
.RS
.PP
themectl export gruvbox-dark all --output ./exports/
.RE
.PP
Export all formats using flag:
.RS
.PP
themectl export gruvbox-dark kitty --all --output ./exports/
.RE
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR themectl (1),
.BR themectl-generators (7)
